title: Alex Pretti remembered by health care workers at a Minneapolis vigil as a ‘stand-up guy’
description: Health care workers brought flowers and wreaths, lit candles, and draped stethoscopes over a wooden cross as a makeshift memorial to nurse Alex Pretti.
